{"tid":196464,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"打飛機射錯人","createTime":"2017-04-11T10:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T15:23:05.000Z","uid":10821,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"737b10131d36a9438807c819ca8cf03810412dfe","tid":196464,"uid":10821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:26:40.000Z","msg":"平時一大早起身見到新聞小珍報新聞[1]<br />\n<br />\n我已經&quot;動L&quot;左既小弟弟就想向佢發炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但為求對小珍既尊重<br />\n<br />\n於是我特登谷左五日唔打飛機<br />\n<br />\n諗住一炮過射俾小珍，俾佢做facial<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日已經谷左五日如箭在弦既小弟弟再忍唔住啦<br />\n<br />\n一開電視，小珍已經係到ready 緊我d面部護理&quot;精&quot;華&quot;液&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我用手將小弟弟好似shotgun咁狂chok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就黎顏射佢既時候...你老母<br />\n<br />\n電視突然轉左做當奴曾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我幾億精兵又忍唔住出左一半，收唔撚番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是一路嗌：哎呀，仆街啦，你老母，呀...呀...呀...呀...呀...<br />\n<br />\n就咁我幾億子彈射左落當奴塊面到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街，而家仲好撚興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，早知下次定住個畫面先射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還番我谷左五日既精兵俾我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2f52f32945737d08061e930c7618d86927c37f","tid":196464,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:27:55.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"dc2ffd532f160caef87391253cee40a86511f52f","tid":196464,"uid":25002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bac0752ebefbc604487aa6901fdd39972b9fcced","tid":196464,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:28:49.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的，重作"},{"pid":"ad4cf97b7c31ad9b5f72d9f1c1e819a1326efe7f","tid":196464,"uid":22599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:31:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8fdf8cb622f1a174cabe5e4bee0bb406afe6406","tid":196464,"uid":103113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"0分"},{"pid":"0cf7aa1f6b3a10a7757bdeb64569ac1dec5758c4","tid":196464,"uid":82528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:28:53.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"f9fed71d2c9b4fb09be8329cb74b570753fa9189","tid":196464,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"無圖😊"},{"pid":"1d174f6e275bcbe22f9d38981c5f0c4ed7fd4f83","tid":196464,"uid":10821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無圖😊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac2f2d8759b98f3d549a39e1bd713720e0cd390","tid":196464,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原本個version係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經唔記得左</blockquote><br />\n射落689到"},{"pid":"8d920149615b24a30a69b612166f447b8d898b64","tid":196464,"uid":15282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:16:30.000Z","msg":"當年上高登睇既第一個post 就係呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\